title: Assembly of HG02109 Haplotype 1
Description: HG02109 haplotype1 assembly generated by the Human Pangenome Reference Consortium using HiC phasing. Mitochondrial sequences are included in haplotype 2. For male samples, chrY sequences are included in haplotype 1 and chrX sequences are included in haplotype 2.
